				</p>
				<p style="font-size:12px; text-align:center; margin:0; color:#555555">
					Filed pursuant to CCP § 8.01 &amp; § 8.02
				</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:14px; text-align:start">&nbsp;</p>

<hr style="background-color:#353c41; color:#353c41; font-size:1px; border:none; height:2px; margin:0">

<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:14px; text-align:start">&nbsp;</p>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     INTRODUCTION
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
{{#if introduction}}
{{paragraphs introduction "background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:16px; text-align:justify"}}
<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:14px; text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>
{{else}}
<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:14px; text-align:justify">
	&nbsp;
</p>

<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:16px; text-align:justify">
	The People of the State of San Andreas, by and through <strong>{{prosecutor.name}}</strong>, {{prosecutor.rank}} for the County of Los Santos, hereby accuse <strong>{{defendant.name}}</strong> of the following crimes, in violation of the laws of the State of San Andreas:
</p>

<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:14px; text-align:justify">
	&nbsp;
</p>
{{/if}}

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     COUNTS
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
{{#each counts}}
<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:13px; text-align:center">
	<span><span style="font-size:17px"><strong><u>COUNT {{math @index "+" 1}}</u></strong></span></span>
</p>

<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:15px; text-align:center; margin:6px 0 10px 0">
	<strong>{{crime}}</strong>
</p>

{{#if justification}}
<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:14px; text-align:justify; padding:0 12px; border-left:3px solid #353c41; margin-left:8px">
	<span style="font-size:15px">{{nl2br justification}}</span>
</p>
{{/if}}

<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:14px">&nbsp;</p>
{{/each}}

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     EVIDENCE
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<hr style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); color:#cbcbcb; font-size:13px; text-align:start">

<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:13px; text-align:center">
	<span><span style="font-size:20px"><b><u>Evidence</u></b></span></span>
</p>

<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:13px; text-align:justify">
	&nbsp;
</p>

<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:16px; text-align:justify">
	The following evidence is submitted in support of this Information and will be made available to the defense pursuant to CCP § 13.01:
</p>

<p style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#353c41; font-size:13px; text-align:justify">
	&nbsp;
</p>

{{#each exhibits}}
